      <section eId="sec_44_12_44">
        <num>44-12-44</num>
        <content>
          <p>In all cases of bailment, after proof of loss by the bailor, the burden of proof is on the bailee to show proper diligence.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2037; Code 1868, § 2038; Code 1873, § 2064; Code 1882, § 2064; Civil Code 1895, § 2896; Civil Code 1910, § 3469; Code 1933, § 12-104.)</p>
